    "author": "조회수:2493",
    "date": "2022-06-02 19:25:24",
    "hit": "2493",
    "content": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:26px;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><u><strong style=\"text-align: center;\">2022년도 여름방학 케이크 데코특강</strong></u></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\"><strong>&nbsp;1. 수업일자</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">-&nbsp; 7월22일(금), 7월29일(금), 8월12일(금)&nbsp; &lt;3회수업&gt;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\"><strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:22px;\">2. 수업시간</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">- 오전11시 ~ 13시</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\">3. 수업료</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">- 15만원( 재료비포함)</span></p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">&nbsp;4. 접수기간</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">- 7월1일 ~ 7월15일</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">&nbsp;<u><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><em>※, 수업 세부내용은 홈페이지 첫화면의 블러그를 참조바랍니다.</em></span></strong></u></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
